data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This like-new 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home is a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. This Beauty is situated on a spacious corner lot in a NO HOA Community. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed open-concept floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring high-end appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening with family, this space is perfect for creating lasting memories. The main level boasts a luxurious master suite, providing a peaceful retreat with its spa-like bathroom and spacious walk-in closet and another mini master with its own private bath. Upstairs there are 2 additional bedrooms and a large bonus room that adds versatility to the floor plan, making it an ideal space for a home office, gym, or media room. Outdoor living is equally impressive with a charming front porch, ideal for sipping morning coffee, and a covered patio with a built-in fireplace for those cool nights. The expansive corner lot offers endless possibilities for gardening and other outdoor activities. This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours – schedule a showing today and experience the magic of this impeccable home!
